<subSubSection id="C3662BAE560CFFB1FF45F982FD4CF92D" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BC37825560CFFB1FF45F982FD4CF92D" blockId="10.[151,1437,1488,1983]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FF45F982FEBEF9C9" bold="true" box="[199,334,1632,1658]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name is derived from Sanskrit, 
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FD72F983FCC3F9C9" box="[752,819,1633,1658]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">tamra</emphasis>
meaning copper, 
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FC7DF983FBCAF9C9" box="[1023,1082,1633,1658]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">varni</emphasis>
meaning coloured, referring to the cupreous sheen on some of the body’s scales.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3662BAE560CFFB1FF45F94AFDCDF80D" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BC37825560CFFB1FF45F94AFDCDF80D" blockId="10.[151,1437,1488,1983]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FF45F94AFEB2F971" bold="true" box="[199,322,1704,1730]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Of the fringed-abdomen species, 
<taxonomicName id="4C7C03A6560CFFB1FD3DF94AFC10F971" authority="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison, 2022" authorityName="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison" authorityYear="2022" box="[703,992,1704,1730]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Stenaelurillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tamravarni" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FD3DF94AFC10F971" box="[703,992,1704,1730]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Stenaelurillus tamravarni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FC65F94AFBB1F971" bold="true" box="[999,1089,1704,1730]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A23B194C560CFFB1FC65F94AFBB1F971" box="[999,1089,1704,1730]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
is unique for the muted colour of the male’s abdomen and the prolaterally-leaning embolus. The male abdomen appears as a brindled greyish brown in the anterior half, composed of a mix of cream and copper scales, much less colourful than the orange of 
<taxonomicName id="4C7C03A6560CFFB1FA05F913FEFAF89D" authorityName="Caleb &amp; Mathai" authorityYear="2016" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Stenaelurillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="metallicus">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FA05F913FEFAF89D" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">S. metallicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C7C03A6560CFFB1FEC2F8F7FE41F89D" authority="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison, 2022" authorityName="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison" authorityYear="2022" box="[320,433,1812,1839]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Stenaelurillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vyaghri" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FEC2F8F7FE41F89D" box="[320,433,1812,1839]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">S. vyaghri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FE3AF8F6FDE1F89D" bold="true" box="[440,529,1812,1838]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A23B194C560CFFB1FE3AF8F6FDE1F89D" box="[440,529,1812,1838]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, and with longer fringes. The embolus differs from 
<taxonomicName id="4C7C03A6560CFFB1FBD0F8F7FB11F89D" authorityName="Caleb &amp; Mathai" authorityYear="2016" box="[1106,1249,1812,1839]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Stenaelurillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="metallicus">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FBD0F8F7FB90F89C" box="[1106,1120,1813,1839]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FBECF8F6FB11F89D" box="[1134,1249,1812,1838]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">metallicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in being thicker, especially basally, and from 
<taxonomicName id="4C7C03A6560CFFB1FE5DF8DBFDA3F8E1" authority="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison, 2022" authorityName="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison" authorityYear="2022" box="[479,595,1848,1875]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Stenaelurillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vyaghri" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FE5DF8DBFDA3F8E1" box="[479,595,1848,1875]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">S. vyaghri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FDDEF8DAFD47F8E1" bold="true" box="[604,695,1848,1874]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A23B194C560CFFB1FDDEF8DAFD47F8E1" box="[604,695,1848,1874]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
in leaning prolaterally and lacking a basal retrolateral cusp. The RTA of 
<taxonomicName id="4C7C03A6560CFFB1FF6CF8BFFE77F8C5" authority="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison, 2022" authorityName="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison" authorityYear="2022" box="[238,391,1885,1911]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Stenaelurillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tamravarni" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FF6CF8BFFE77F8C5" box="[238,391,1885,1911]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">S. tamravarni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FE0CF8BEFE17F8C5" bold="true" box="[398,487,1884,1910]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A23B194C560CFFB1FE0CF8BEFE17F8C5" box="[398,487,1884,1910]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
is longer than that of 
<taxonomicName id="4C7C03A6560CFFB1FD5BF8BFFC97F8C5" authorityName="Caleb &amp; Mathai" authorityYear="2016" box="[729,871,1884,1911]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Stenaelurillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="metallicus">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FD5BF8BFFC97F8C5" box="[729,871,1884,1911]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">S. metallicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, more pointed than that of 
<taxonomicName id="4C7C03A6560CFFB1FB16F8BFFAF5F8C5" authority="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison, 2022" authorityName="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison" authorityYear="2022" box="[1172,1285,1884,1911]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Stenaelurillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vyaghri" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FB16F8BFFAF5F8C5" box="[1172,1285,1884,1911]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">S. vyaghri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FA89F8BEFA94F8C5" bold="true" box="[1291,1380,1884,1910]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A23B194C560CFFB1FA89F8BEFA94F8C5" box="[1291,1380,1884,1910]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
. The female of 
<taxonomicName id="4C7C03A6560CFFB1FE8AF863FE52F829" authority="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison, 2022" authorityName="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison" authorityYear="2022" box="[264,418,1921,1947]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Stenaelurillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tamravarni" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FE8AF863FE52F829" box="[264,418,1921,1947]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">S. tamravarni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FE2BF862FDF3F829" bold="true" box="[425,515,1920,1946]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A23B194C560CFFB1FE2BF862FDF3F829" box="[425,515,1920,1946]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
has markings with less contrast than those of 
<taxonomicName id="4C7C03A6560CFFB1FB87F863FB64F829" authorityName="Caleb &amp; Mathai" authorityYear="2016" box="[1029,1172,1920,1947]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Stenaelurillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="metallicus">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FB87F863FBE3F828" box="[1029,1043,1921,1947]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FBA3F862FB64F829" box="[1057,1172,1920,1946]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">metallicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C7C03A6560CFFB1FB49F863FACCF829" authority="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison, 2022" authorityName="Marathe &amp; Sanap &amp; Joglekar &amp; Caleb &amp; Maddison" authorityYear="2022" box="[1227,1340,1920,1947]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Stenaelurillus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vyaghri" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FB49F863FB29F828" box="[1227,1241,1921,1947]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FB64F862FACCF829" box="[1254,1340,1920,1946]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">vyaghri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B908A437560CFFB1FAC1F862FA6CF829" bold="true" box="[1347,1436,1920,1946]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A23B194C560CFFB1FAC1F862FA6CF829" box="[1347,1436,1920,1946]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
with abdominal spots quite indistinct.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
